# Pangolin vault files (encrypted user data — never commit even though
# the AEAD-sealed contents are protected at rest; metadata + structure
# would still leak, and a committed vault surprises verifiers)
*.pvf
*.pvf-wal
*.pvf-shm
*.pvf.lock

